description: Experience urban luxury in this top-floor, 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom South Boston condo. Enjoy a cozy living area featuring a gas fireplace, and step out onto a private balcony through sliding glass door. The open-concept kitchen is a chef's delight, with a spacious island, stainless steel appliances, dining area, and gleaming hardwood floors throughout. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet and a full en-suite bathroom. A unique spiral staircase is your exclusive access to the roof. Currently just a vision, but potential for new owner to build a roof deck where you can entertain guests while enjoying stunning Boston city views. Located in a tranquil neighborhood, this home is just minutes from Carson Beach and Joe Moakley Park. The condo includes in-unit laundry, central air, and extra basement storage. With convenient access to Interstates 90 and 93, this property is a must-see for its perfect blend of urban living and peaceful atmosphere. Opportunity for all owners and investors!
